---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About | ByteLite LLC"
  description="ByteLite LLC is a founder-led company from Helena, Montana building privacy-first products and private deterministic systems research."
  keywords="About ByteLite LLC, Helena Montana, founder-led, Tash Broadwater"
  
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>ByteLite LLC</h1>
      <p class="about-sub">
        A founder-led company building privacy-first products and deterministic structure
        infrastructure from Helena, Montana.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Company story -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">The Company</p>
        <h2>One founder. Four projects. Clear status.</h2>
        <p style="margin-top:1.25rem;font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.8;">
          ByteLite LLC was founded in 2024 by Tash Broadwater in Helena, Montana.
          The company started with HeartStrings — a consent-first adult social board game
          that became the first public-facing product direction.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:1rem;font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.8;">
          Alongside HeartStrings, the company expanded into private research on deterministic
          structure infrastructure, visual inspection, reasoning interfaces, movement, cost,
          and governed action. That research continues privately with no public product claims
          until validation is complete.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:1rem;font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.8;">
          ByteLite LLC is proof-gated: product claims are made only when they can be defended.
          The public site intentionally separates product status from research status.
          The Architecture page explains the system design and claim boundaries without
          disclosing proprietary mechanisms.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-cards">
        <div class="card about-info-card">
          <div class="about-info-label">Founded</div>
          <div class="about-info-value">2024</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card about-info-card">
          <div class="about-info-label">Location</div>
          <div class="about-info-value">Helena, Montana</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card about-info-card">
          <div class="about-info-label">Structure</div>
          <div class="about-info-value">Solo-founder LLC</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card about-info-card">
          <div class="about-info-label">Public product</div>
          <div class="about-info-value">HeartStrings Play<br/><span style="font-size:.875rem;color:#7b829e;">Pre-launch</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Product overview -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Products &amp; Projects</p>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">What ByteLite LLC is building.</h2>
      <div class="about-products">
        <div class="card about-product">
          <div class="ap-header">
            <h3 style="color:#f472b6;">HeartStrings Play</h3>
            <span class="badge badge-prelaunch">Pre-launch</span>
          </div>
          <p>Premium adult social board game for private groups. Consent-first. 2–18 players. 350 cards. Six escalation tiers. Three board versions. Manufacturing preparation underway.</p>
          <a href="/heartstrings" class="ap-link">See HeartStrings Play &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card about-product">
          <div class="ap-header">
            <h3 style="color:#818cf8;">HeartStrings App</h3>
            <span class="badge badge-private">Private beta</span>
          </div>
          <p>Private-test digital companion for the HeartStrings ecosystem. Profiles, onboarding, and future social features in development. No public app store release.</p>
          <a href="/heartstrings-app" class="ap-link">See HeartStrings App &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card about-product">
          <div class="ap-header">
            <h3 style="color:#6366f1;">ByteLite Research</h3>
            <span class="badge badge-research">Private research</span>
          </div>
          <p>Private infrastructure research into deterministic data representation and verification systems. No public product. Mechanisms intentionally not disclosed during validation.</p>
          <a href="/research" class="ap-link">See Research &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card about-product">
          <div class="ap-header">
            <h3 style="color:#a78bfa;">Deep Kore / AIya</h3>
            <span class="badge badge-research">Private research</span>
          </div>
          <p>Private reasoning research and guide concept. Not a public AI product. Safety-first principles govern all development. No public product.</p>
          <a href="/research#deep-kore" class="ap-link">See Research &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Architecture CTA -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;text-align:center;">
      <p class="eyebrow">Deterministic Structure</p>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">The Architecture.</h2>
      <p style="font-size:1.0625rem;color:#7b829e;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        The Architecture page explains how ByteLite LLC approaches deterministic structure,
        reasoning, governance, and proof-gated development — without disclosing trade-secret
        mechanisms.
      </p>
      <a href="/architecture" class="btn btn-outline">Explore the Architecture</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partnership Constraints -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
      <p class="eyebrow">Partnerships</p>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Partnership Constraints</h2>
      <p style="font-size:1.0625rem;color:#7b829e;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Core research is handled with strict IP control, private validation boundaries,
        and proof-gated disclosure. ByteLite LLC is open to serious diligence conversations,
        but does not expose private mechanisms publicly during validation.
      </p>
      <div class="about-inquiries">
        <h4 style="color:#e4e7f2;margin-bottom:1rem;">For inquiries:</h4>
        <div class="inquiry-list">
          <div class="inquiry-item">
            <span class="inquiry-dot" style="background:#f472b6;"></span>
            <span>HeartStrings Play pre-launch interest</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inquiry-item">
            <span class="inquiry-dot" style="background:#6366f1;"></span>
            <span>Controlled research partnerships</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inquiry-item">
            <span class="inquiry-dot" style="background:#34d399;"></span>
            <span>Investor conversations</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inquiry-item">
            <span class="inquiry-dot" style="background:#a78bfa;"></span>
            <span>Private validation discussions</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top:2rem;">Contact ByteLite LLC</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact CTA -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container cta-block-simple">
      <h2>Get in touch.</h2>
      <p>Partnership inquiries, HeartStrings pre-launch interest, research conversations, and investor discussions are all welcome.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact ByteLite LLC</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>

<style>

.about-hero { padding: 5.5rem 0 4rem; }
.about-hero h1 { max-width: 480px; }
.about-sub { max-width: 560px; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.0625rem; color: #7b829e; line-height: 1.75; }
.about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
@media (max-width: 900px) { .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; } }
.about-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
.about-info-card { padding: 1.25rem; }
.about-info-label { font-size: .75rem; color: #4a5068; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; margin-bottom: .375rem; }
.about-info-value { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; color: #e4e7f2; line-height: 1.4; }
.about-products { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }
@media (max-width: 767px) { .about-products { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
.about-product { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .875rem; }
.ap-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: .75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.ap-link { font-size: .875rem; font-weight: 500; color: #818cf8; margin-top: auto; }
.ap-link:hover { color: #a5b4fc; }
.cta-block-simple { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 0; }
.cta-block-simple h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.cta-block-simple p { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; font-size: 1.0625rem; }
.about-inquiries { background: #0d1120; border: 1px solid #1a2235; border-radius: .75rem; padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem; }
.inquiry-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .625rem; }
.inquiry-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .75rem; font-size: .9375rem; color: #a0a8c0; }
.inquiry-dot { width: .5rem; height: .5rem; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }

</style>
